tests.name: Troubleshooting this autograder
tests.run:
printf -- "The grader for this seeks to do one thing and one thing only: build your app.

If you are failing this autograder test, it is because your app will not build.

To test this yourself, which you should already be doing, go to the root of your
repository directory and then run the build script yourself. To do this, run:

  npm run build

If that returns erors, then the autograder will not pass.

Your job then is to figure out what is causing the errors.
"
